{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5754f545ed","title":"关于彻底粉碎陈诚向鲁南进攻的建议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f7dcb82f6","index":0,"year":1947,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"5754f545ed","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"许世友","id":"c2f8307fbd","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji4.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"1b09f4b97a","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"a2c9e64dee","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":8,"text":"陈诚（一八九八——一九六五），浙江青田人。当时任国民党军参谋总长。"},{"id":"dd4669a96f","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":7,"text":"陈饶张黎，指陈毅、饶漱石、张云逸、黎玉，当时分别任华东军区司令员、政治委员、副司令员和副政治委员。粟谭，指粟裕、谭震林，当时分别任华东野战军副司令员和副政治委员。"},{"id":"6ffa9bbd09","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":3,"offset":26,"text":"王建安（一九○七——一九八○），湖北黄安（今红安）人，当时任华东野战军第八纵队司令员。许世友（一九○五——一九八五），河南新县人，当时任华东野战军第九纵队司令员。宋时轮，当时任华东野战军第十纵队司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5fd0779379","type":"title","text":"关于彻底粉碎陈诚向鲁南进攻的建议","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2c9e64dee","type":"appellation","text":"陈饶张黎，粟谭：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd4669a96f","type":"paragraph","text":"为着彻底粉碎陈诚向鲁南之进攻，请你们注意下列各点：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ffa9bbd09","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）集中绝对优势兵力，你们将王建安、许世友、宋时轮三部南调是很对的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74fa8d069d","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）休整部队，利用敌大举进攻前夜全军休整，多一天好一天，休整即是胜利。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"944bdc3ad6","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）诱敌深入，敌不动我不打，敌不进到有利于我、不利于敌之地点我亦不打，完全立于主动地位。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"848835bec1","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）先打弱者，后打强者，可能进攻之敌二十二个旅中，战力较强者约八个旅，较弱者约十四个旅。如我能首先歼灭较弱之十四个旅，此次进攻即算打破，然后再歼较强之八个旅，便很从容。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01766af4d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）每次歼敌不要超过四个旅，最好是三个旅，一则保证速胜，二则手中留有未使用的大量兵力，可以接着打第二仗。这即是说，将你们手中的全部兵力分为两个集团，轮番作战与休息，准备在一个半月至两个月内连续不断打七八个大仗，彻底粉碎敌之进攻。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1e70c2fb6","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点，当作建议，究应如何办理最为妥善，请按实情决定。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2621c389ed","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9d62a9733","type":"paragraph","text":"丑江","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"5754f545ed","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":241,"end":240}}}},"__N_SSG":true}